title: Traditional vs SEP IRA: What You Need to Know as an Entrepreneur
subtitle: Explore the differences between Traditional IRAs and SEP IRAs, and find out how entrepreneurs can maximize their retirement savings.
content:
Son, did you open that traditional IRA like I told you to?

No, I did not.

And why not?

Because I'm an entrepreneur now, Dad. I opened a SEP IRA where I can contribute ten times what you can to your little traditional IRA.

And that $61K is all deductible?

Yup.

Don't you have to also contribute to your employees' plans?

If I had employees, yes, but I'm a Fortnite strategy consultant, Dad. I work odd hours, and I work alone.
